        <lg type="poem">
          <head>1L: Still as ünnern warme Dęk</head>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>Still as ünnern warme Dęk</l>
            <l>Liggt dat Dörp in witten Snee,</l>
            <l>Mank de Ellern slöppt de Bęk,</l>
            <l>Ünnert Is de blanke See.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>Wicheln stat in witte Haar,</l>
            <l>Spegelt slapri all de Köpp,</l>
            <l>All is ruhi, kold un klar,</l>
            <l>As de Dod, de ewi slöppt.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>Wit, so wit de Ogen reckt,</l>
            <l>Nich en Lęben, nich en Lut;</l>
            <l>Blau na'n blauen Hęben treckt</l>
            <l>Sach de Rok nan Snee herut.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg rhyme="unknown" type="stanza">
            <l>Ik much slapen, as de Bom,</l>
            <l>Sünner Weh un sünner Lust,</l>
            <l>Doch dar treckt mi as in Drom</l>
            <l>Still de Rok to Hus.</l>
          </lg>
